OL,7,FMs Archibald has previously warned
OL,8,Fthat failure to balance the budget by
OL,9,Fthe end of the financial year would
OL,10,Fsee the Government withdraw a previous
OL,11,Foffer to write off #559million worth
OL,12,Fof debt owed to the Treasury.
OL,14,FThe budgetary over-commitments were
OL,15,Fraised during Assembly questions on
OL,16,FMonday.
