OL,4,C'dire' for broader Executive - Finance
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,F"Obviously, all ministers are
OL,8,Fautonomous within their own
OL,9,Fdepartments and they have to take
OL,10,Fdecisions to live responsibly.
OL,12,F"But I think that the consequences of
OL,13,Fany department overspending this year
OL,14,Fare dire for the Executive as a whole,
OL,15,Fin relation to the fact that the over-
OL,16,Fcommitted funding would come off next
OL,17,Fyear's budget, and would also put into
OL,18,Fquestion the write-off of the
OL,19,F#559million of what the Treasury
OL,20,Fcalled debt from previous years.
